      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWIFT BREE (1) hit the frame last time at this track but the start prior rocketed around 527m at this track in 30.33. Looks the one to beat on win two back. ELSA ABOVE (4) was below best at her last start when 6th at Wentworth Park following a win (24.88) at this track two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from six starts. Should be in this for a long way. ARMATREE VIOLET (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 19.62 beating Rosacky Rayo. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Significant danger. MOTOR CITY SONNY (3) form at this course and distance reads well.",
